    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[故事]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是吸血鬼城堡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不知情的旅行者来到这里</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吸血鬼A笑了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哦，看看我们的美味佳肴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲爱的，我怎么能吓到你呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我迫不及待地想看到他们脸上惊恐和绝望的表情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.poster.avif?t=1771567021\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.webm?t=1771567021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169250/extras/43474d764517e65855af5f4226242ca3.mp4?t=1771567021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[概述].</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款躲避吸血鬼的生存逃生游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >躲在阴影中，避免被吸血鬼发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在豪宅中找到逃生所需的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找可以藏身的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细听，因为敌人越靠近，脚步声就越大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果听到声音，就躲在阴影里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您能活着回来吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
